<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Profil Muhammad Rezky Maulana</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #4CAF50, #2E7D32);
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    padding:20px;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    width:100%;
    max-width:700px;
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:30px;
    text-align:center;
    box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

.avatar{
    width:140px;
    height:140px;
    margin:auto;
    border-radius:15px;
    background:#4CAF50;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    font-size:70px;
}

h1{
    margin-top:20px;
    color:#2E7D32;
}

.age{
    margin-top:10px;
    color:#666;
}

.section{
    margin-top:25px;
}

.section h2{
    color:#2E7D32;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

p{
    line-height:1.7;
}

.minecraft-box{
    margin-top:20px;
    background:#e8f5e9;
    border-left:6px solid #2E7D32;
    padding:15px;
    border-radius:10px;
}

footer{
    margin-top:25px;
    color:#777;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

    <div class="avatar">⛏️</div>

    <h1>Muhammad Rezky Maulana</h1>
    <p class="age">16 Tahun</p>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Tentang Saya</h2>
        <p>
            Halo! Nama saya Muhammad Rezky Maulana.
            Saya berusia 16 tahun dan memiliki hobi bermain game.
            Saya suka mencoba berbagai game petualangan dan survival.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Game Favorit</h2>
        <div class="minecraft-box">
            <strong>Minecraft</strong><br>
            Saya suka bermain Minecraft karena bisa membangun,
            menjelajah dunia, bertahan hidup, dan bermain bersama teman.
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        © 2026 Muhammad Rezky Maulana
    </footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>
